  "StockRole": "Brawler",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Ziegfried came out of the pre-Civil War Commonwealth procurement period, when both halves of the Federated Commonwealth were still trying to field hardware that impressed the other side, and Kallon delivered something genuinely clever with the TSM integration. After the split, both the Lyran Alliance and the Federated Suns ended up running it, which led to the unusual situation of identical machines facing each other across the front lines. A heavy mech that deliberately runs hot as part of its combat plan requires a very specific kind of pilot discipline to use properly, but when it works the Sword hits hard enough to end engagements quickly.",
